.TH MNEMOSYNE-WIKI-SEMANTIC-CONTRADICTIONS 1 "2026-06-23" "mnemosyne" "Mnemosyne CLI"
.SH NAME
mnemosyne wiki-semantic-contradictions \- Opt\-in local semantic contradiction discovery.
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmnemosyne wiki-semantic-contradictions\fR [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opt\-in local semantic contradiction discovery.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-wiki\-root\fR
LLM Wiki root (default: ~/mnemosyne/wiki)
.TP
\fB\-\-db\-path\fR
KnowledgeGraph DB path
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR
.TP
\fB\-\-lock\-timeout\fR
Seconds to wait for the wiki write lock on write commands
.TP
\fB\-\-write\fR
Persist review candidates
.TP
\fB\-\-include\-raw\-excerpts\fR
Opt in to bounded redacted raw source excerpts for local files
.SH SEE ALSO
mnemosyne(1)
